</teiHeader><facsimile><graphic url="https://www.e-manuscripta.ch/i3f/v20/1038286/manifest"/></facsimile><text><body><div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038287" n="127r"/>
<opener>
<lb/>Ad <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelottum.</rs>
<lb/>Vir Excellentissime, Fautor honoratissime.
      </opener>
<p>
<lb/>Accepi heri <rs key="B_991170517054705501" type="letter">literas</rs> Tuas humanissimas <date when="1714-03-10">10. Martii</date> scriptas, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> exoptatissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mum nuntium mihi attulere de felici laborum tuorum in negotio Patavino
         <lb/>successu, co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endationes enim tuas tantum apud <abbr>Illmos</abbr> et <abbr>Excellmos</abbr> <rs type="organisation">Studii</rs>
<lb/>Patavini Dominos <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatores</rs> pondus habuisse, ut brevi me electum et ad
         <lb/>cathedram Mathematicam <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavium</rs> evocatum iri confidas, l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus intelligo.
         <lb/>Non possum quin gratias tibi persolvam maximas, quod tanto fervore mihi
         <lb/>prodesse et maximas qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> se offerunt difficultates superare studeas<subst><del>,</del><add>.</add></subst> Habebis me
         <lb/>beneficii tanti semper memorem, maximoque me obstringe<subst><del>ns</del><add>s</add></subst> vinculo, si ut<del> porro</del>
         <lb/>favorem suum mihi porro conservent Illustrissimi <rs type="persons">Viri</rs> quos in partes nostras
         <lb/>traxisti, efficere non desinas; gratum meum in Te animum per promta
<lb/>obsequia declarare studebo. <rs key="B_991170517055205501" type="letter">Responsionem</rs> ad priores Tuas <rs type="letters" key="B_991170517055605501 B_991170517055305501">epistolas</rs>,
         <lb/>quam ob varia negotia citius exarare non poteram, dedi <date when="1714-02-14">14. die Februarii</date>,
      <lb/>hanc autem Te non accepisse ex ultimis <rs type="letter" key="B_991170517054905501">Tuis</rs> non sine dolore percepi;
      <lb/>Verba ejus <rs type="letter" key="B_991170517054905501">responsi</rs> ne pereant omnino, huc transcribere volui; En ipso<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum tenorem <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#pp">pp.</g></orig><reg>etc.</reg></choice></abbr><note type="editorial">Die Zusammenfassung der zwei in der Abfertigung verlorenen Briefe wurde von Nic. I B. hier im Entwurf weggelassen.</note> Hoc fuit responsum meum. Eodem die <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs>
<lb/>meus et ego <rs  type="letters" key="B_991170514861105501 B_991170517058605501">literas</rs> misimus ad <abbr>Illmum</abbr> Abbatem <rs key="pers_DE-588-119291967" type="person">Fardellam</rs>, quas etiam
         <lb/>intercidisse suspicamur, quod num ita sit forte ex ipso scire poteris,
         <lb/>gratum facies, si salutem ipsi nostro nomine atque gratias pro officiis mi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>hi pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stitis testificaberis, quando ejus rei faciend<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> occasio se Tibi obtulerit.
         <lb/>Fluidorum pressiones obliqu<subst><del>as</del><add><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add></subst> sunt in duplicata ratione sinuum an<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gulorum incidenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, singulorum enim globulorum pressio obliqua
         <lb/>ad eorundem globulorum eadem velocitate normaliter incidentium
         <pb facs="1038288" n="127v"/>
<lb/>pressionem eam rationem habet, quam sinus anguli incidenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad sin<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
         <lb/>totum, deinde <subst><del>et</del><add>ea</add></subst>ndem etiam rationem habet numerus globulorum in
         <lb/>certam et determinatam vasis continentis portionem determinato aliquo
         <lb/>tempore oblique incurrentium ad numerum globulorum eodem tempo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re in eandem portionem normaliter incurrentium. <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> meus in
         <lb/><rs key="biblio_RTB4565Q" type="biblio">libro</rs> quem nuper edidit cui titulus, Essai d'une nouvelle <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#pp">pp.</g></orig><reg>etc.</reg></choice></abbr> hac propo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sitione tanquam principio usus est ad resistentiam aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> et vim ven<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>torum in naves determinandum. Hujus <rs key="biblio_RTB4565Q" type="biblio">libri</rs> exemplar Tibi trans<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mitti curabit <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs>, ut saltem aliquo modo demonstret, quam accepta
         <lb/>sibi sit amicitia Tua. Gratum faceres si co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>odam nobis subministrare
         <lb/>posses occasionem <rs key="biblio_RTB4565Q" type="biblio">librum</rs> hunc, ut et eos de quibus supra mentionem
         <lb/>feci, <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetias</rs> transmittendi, ea enim raro admodum et difficulter
<lb/>hic <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> se nobis offert.
      </p>
<closer>Interim Vale salutatus quamplurimum
         <lb/> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruo</rs> meo, quem ad qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>vis officia nunquam non paratissimum
         <lb/>habebis. <dateline><rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <date when="1714-03-28">28. Martii 1714</date>.</dateline>
<lb/><abbr>Illmi</abbr> et <abbr>Excellmi</abbr> Nominis Tui
         <lb/>Cultor Devotissimus <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person"><abbr>N. B.</abbr></rs>
</closer>
</div></body></text></TEI>